heading: Ruins of Eridu Dungeon Guide
content: Ruins of Eridu does not feature any dangerous monsters, and has a linear, yet convoluted layout that requires some backtracking. It is solid for farming, but is not currently a possible . Spiritcaller of Flames is an easy meat piñata boss. This dungeon unlocks the , a decent offensive aspect for the Necromancer. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
